hadiths[65]{hadithnumber,text}:
3091,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, jange-badr ke maale-ghanimat se mere hissey mein aik jawan ontni aai thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi aik jawan ontni khums ke maal mein se di thi, jab mera irada hua ke Fatima (Raziallahu anha) binte-rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shadi karun to bani qainuqaa' ( qabila yahood (ke aik sahib se jo sunaar they, maine ye tay kya ke wo mere sath chaley aur ham donon izkhir ghaas (jangal se) laaein. mera irada ye tha ke main wo ghaas sunaaron ko beech doonga aur uski qeemat se apne nikah ka walima karunga. abhi main un donon oontniyon ka saamaan, paalaan aur thailey aur rassiyaan jama kar raha tha aur ye donon oontniyan aik Ansari sahabi ke ghar ke paas baithi hui thin ke jab Sara saman faraaham karke wapas aaya to kya dekhta hun ke meri donon oontniyon ke kohan kisi ne kaat diye hain. aur unke pet cheer kar andar se kalejii nikal li gaee hain. jab maine ye haal dekha to main be ikhtiyar ro diya. maine puchha ke ye sab kuchh kis ne kya hai? to logon ne bataya ke Hamza-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur wo usi ghar mein kuchh Ansar ke sath sharab pi rahe hain. main wahan se wapas aa gaya aur seedha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. aap ki khidmat mein us waqt Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) bhi baithey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey dekhtey hi samajh gaey ke main kisi badey sadmey mein hun. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya : ''Ali! kya hua?'' maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! maine aaj ke din jaisa sadma kabhi nahi dekha. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne meri donon oontniyon par zulm kar diya. donon ke kohan kaat daley aur unke pet cheer daley. abhi wo usi ghar mein kai yaaron ke sath sharab ki majlis jamaaey huey maujood hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar apni chadar mangi aur usey odh kar paidal chalney lagey. main aur Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke peechhey-peechhey huey. aakhir jab wo ghar aa gaya jis mein Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they, to aap ne andar aaney ki ijazat chahi aur andar maujood logon ne aapko ijazat de di. wo log sharab pi rahe they. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo kuchh kya tha. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein kuchh malaamat karna shuru ki. Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki aankhen sharab ke nashey mein makhmoor aur surkh ho rahi thin. unhon-ne nazar utha kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha. phir nazar zara aur uper uthaaii, phir wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghutnon par nazar le gaey iske baad nigaah aur utha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki naaf ke qareeb dekhney lagey. phir chehrey par jama di. phir kehney lagey ke tum sab mere bap ke ghulam ho, ye haal dekh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab mehsus kya ke Hamza bilkul nashey mein hain, to aap wahin se ultey paon wapas aagey aur ham bhi aap ke sath nikal aaey."
3092,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) se mutalba kya tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us tarka se unhein unki meeraas ka hissa dilaya jaey jo Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Faiy ki sura mein diya tha (jaisey fidak wghaira).
3093,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apni hayaat mein) farmaya tha ke hamara (garoh anbiya (Alaihissalam) ka ( wirsa taqseem nahi hota, hamara tarka sadqa hai. Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ye sun kar ghussa ho gain aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se tarake-mulaaqaat ki aur wafat tak unse na milein. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad chh mahiney zinda rahi thin. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khaibar aur fidak aur Madina ke sadqey ki wiraasat ka mutalba Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) se kya tha Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko us se inkar tha. unhon-ne kaha ke main kisi bhi aisey amal ko nahi chhod sakta jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni zindagi mein kartey rahe they. (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka Madina ka jo sadqa tha wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko (apne daure-khilaafat mein) de diya. albatta khaibar aur fidak ki jaaidaad ko umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne rok rakha aur farmaya ke ye donon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sadqa hain aur un huquq ke liye jo waqti taur par pesh aatey ya waqti haadsaat ke liye rakhi thin. ye jaaidaad us shakhs ke ikhtiyar mein rahengii jo khaleefae-waqt ho. Zohri ne kaha, chunanche un donon jaaydaadon ka intizam aaj tak (bazariey hukoomat) isi tarah hota chala aata hai."
3094,"(Zohri ne bayan kya ke) Muhammad-bin-Jubair ne mujh se (usi aaney waali) hadis ka zikr kya tha. isliye maine Maalik-bin-Aos ki khidmat mein khud hazir ho kar unse us hadis ke mutaalliq (bataur tasdeeq) poochha. unhon-ne kaha ke din chadh aaya tha aur main apne ghar walon ke sath betha hua tha, itney mein Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik bulaney wala mere paas aaya aur kaha ke ameerul-momineen aapko bula rahe hain. main us qaasid ke sath hi chala gaya aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. aap aik takht par boriyaa bichhaaey, boriye par koi bichhonaa na tha, sirf aik chamdey ke takiye par tek lagaey huey they. main salam karke baith gaya. phir unhon-ne farmaya, Maalik! tumhari qaum ke kuchh log mere paas aaey they, maine unke liye kuchh haqeer si imdaad ka faisla kar liya hai. tum usey apni nigrani mein unmein taqseem kara do, maine arz kya, ya ameerul-momineen! agar aap us kaam par kisi aur ko muqarrar farma detey to behtar hota. lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahi israar kya ke nahi, apni hi tahweel mein baant do. abhi main wahin hazir tha ke ameerul-momineen ke darbaan Yarfaa aaey aur kaha ke Usmaan-bin-Affaan, Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf, Zubair-bin-Awaam aur Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) andar aaney ki ijazat chahtey hain? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke haan, unhein andar bila lo. aap ki ijazat par ye hazraat dakhil huey aur salam karke baith gaey. Yarfaa bhi thodi der baithey rahe aur phir andar aa kar arz kya Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi andar aaney ki ijazat hai? aap ne farmaya ke haan, unhein bhi andar bula lo. aap ki ijazat par ye hazraat bhi andar tashrif ley aaey aur salam karke baith gaey. Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ya ameerul-momineen! mera aur unka faisla kar dijiye. un hazraat ka jhagdaa us jaaidaad ke barey mein tha jo Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bani Nazir ke amwaal mein se (khums ke taur par) inayat farmai thi. is par Usman aur unke sath jo doosrey sahaba they kehney lagey, haan, ameerul-momineen! un hazraat mein faisla farma dijiye aur har aik ko doosrey ki taraf se be-fikr kar dijiye. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, achchha, to phir zara thahariye aur dam ley lijiye mein aap logon se us Allah ki qism de kar poochhta hun jiske hukm se aasman aur zameen qaaim hain. kya aap logon ko malum hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke ''ham paighambaron ka koi waaris nahi hota, jo kuchh ham ( anbiya ( chhod kar jatey hain wo sadqa hota hai.''jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad khud apni zaate-giraamii bhi thi. un hazraat ne tasdeeq ki, ke ji haan, beshak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha. ab umr (Raziallahu anhu) , Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mukhaatab huey, unse poochha. main aap hazraat ko Allah ki qism deta hun, kya aap hazraat ko bhi malum hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa farmaya hai ya nahi? unhon-ne bhi uski tasdeeq ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne beshak aisa farmaya hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab main aap logon se us mamla ki sharah (explaination) bayan karta hun. baat ye hai ke Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye us ghaneemat ka aik makhsoos hissey muqarrar kar diya tha. jisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi kisi doosrey ko nahi diya tha. phir aap ne us aayat ki tilawat ki وما أفاء الله على رسوله منهم‏ se Allah Taala ke irshad ( qadeer ( tak aur wo hissey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye khas raha. magar qism Allah ki ye jaaidaad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum ko chhod kar apne liye jod na rakhii, na khas apne kharch mein laaey, balke tum hi logon ko diin aur tumharey hi kaamon mein kharch kin. ye jo jaaidaad bach rahi hai is mein se aap apni beeviyon ka saal bhar ka kharch liya kartey iske baad jo baqi bachta wo Allah ke maal mein Sharik kar detey (jihad ke saman jutaaney mein) khair Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to apni zindagi mein aisa hi kartey rahe. haaziriin tum ko Allah ki qism ! kya tum ye nahi jantey ? unhon-ne kaha beshak jantey hain. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, main aap hazraat se bhi qism de kar poochhta hun, kya aap log ye nahi jantey hain? ( donon hazraat ne jawab diya haan!) phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne yun farmaya ke phir Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko duniya se utha liya to Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khaleefa hun, aur isliye unhon-ne (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki us mukhlis) jaaidaad par qabza kya aur jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein masaarif kya kartey they, wo kartey rahe. Allah khub janta hai ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apne us tarze-amal mein sachey mukhlis, neku-kaar aur haq ki pairwi karne waley they. phir Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi apne paas bula liya aur ab main Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka naaib muqarrar hua. meri khilafat ko 2 saal ho gaey hain. aur maine bhi us jaaidaad ko apni tahweel mein rakha hai. jo kharchey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) usmein kya kartey they waisaa hi mein bhi karta raha aur Allah khub janta hai ke main apne us tarze-amal mein sachchaa, mukhlis aur haq ki pairwi karne wala hun. phir aap donon mere paas mujh se guftgu karne aaey aur ittifaq se guftgu karne lagey ke donon ka maqsad aik tha. janab Abbaas! aap to isliye tashrif laey ke aapko apne bhatijey (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki meeraas ka dawa mere samney pesh karna tha. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke aap isliye tashrif laey ke aapko apni biwi (Faatima (Raziallahu anhu)) ka dawa pesh karna tha ke unke walid (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ki meeraas unhein milnii chaahiye, maine aap donon hazraat se arz kar diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud farma gaey ke ham paighambaron ki koi meeraas taqseem nahi hoti, ham jo kuchh chhod jatey hain wo sadqa hota hai. phir mujh ko ye munasib malum hua ke main un jaaydaadon ko tumharey qabzey mein de dun, to maine tum se kaha, dekho agar tum chaho to main ye jaaidaad tumharey sipurd kar deta hun, lekin is ahad aur is iqrar par ke tum uski aamadni se wo sab kaam kartey rahogey jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) apni khilafat mein kartey rahe aur jo kaam main apni hukumat ke shuru se karta raha. tum ne is shart ko qabool karke darkhaast ki ke jaaydaadein ham ko de do. maine isi shart par de di, haaziriin kaho maine ye jaaydaadein isi shart par unke hawale ki hain ya nahi? unhon-ne kaha, beshak isi shart par aap ne di hain. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya, main tum ko Allah ki qism deta hun, maine isi shart par ye jaaydaadein aap hazraat ke hawale ki hain ya nahi? unhon-ne kaha beshak. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, phir mujh se kis baat ka faisla chahtey ho? (kya jaaidaad ko taqseem karaanaa chahtey ho) qism Allah ki! jiske hukm se zameen aur aasman qaaim hain main to iske siwa aur koi faisla karne wala nahi. haan ! ye aur baat hai ke agar tum se iska intizam nahi ho sakta to phir jaaidaad mere sipurd kar do. mein iska bhi kaam dekh loonga."
3095,"qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad (darbaare-risaalat mein) hazir hua aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! hamara talluq qabila Rabee se hai aur qabila Muzar ke kuffaar hamarey aur aap ke beech mein baste hain. (is liye unke khatrey ki wjah se ham log) aap ki khidmat mein sirf adab waley mahinon mein hazir ho saktey hain. aap hamein koi aisa waazeh hukm farma dein jis par ham khud bhi mazbootii se qaaim rahen aur jo log hamarey sath nahi aa sakey hain unhein bhi bata dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main tumhen char chizon ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa hun (main tumhen hukm deta hun) Allah par eman laney ka ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath ko girah lagaaii, Namaz qaaim karne ka, zakat dene ka, Ramazan ke rozey rakhney ka, aur is baat ka ke jo kuchh bhi tumhen ghaneemat ka maal miley. usmein panchwan hissey (khums) Allah ke liye nikal do aur tumhen main dabaa, naqeer, hantam aur muzaffat ke istemal se roktaa hun."
3096,"ham se Abdullaah-bin-Yoosuf ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko imam Malik-bin-Anas ne bayan kya, unhein abu-Zinaad ne bayan kya, unhein Aaraj ne aur unhein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke ""merey waaris merey baad aik deenaar bhii na baantein (meraa tarkaa taqseem na karein) main jo chhod jaun usmein se merey aamilon (governaron) ki tankhaah aur meri beeviyon ka kharch nikaalkar baqi sab sadqaa hai."""
3097,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to mere ghar mein aadhey wasq jo ke siwa jo aik taaq mein rakhey huey they aur koi cheez aisi nahi thi jo kisi jigar waley ( jaandaar ( ki khuraak bin sakti . main usi mein se khaatii rahi aur bahut din guzar gaey. phir maine usmein se naap kar nikaalnaa shuru kya to wo jaldi khatm ho gaey.
3098,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apni wafat ke baad) apne hathiyar , aik safaid khachchar , aur aik zameen jisey aap khud sadqa kar gaey they, ke siwa aur koi tarka nahi chhoda tha."
3099,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke) maut ke marz mein) jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka marz bahut badh gaya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sab beeviyon se uski ijazat chahi ke marz ke din aap mere ghar mein guzaarein . lihaza uski ijazat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mil gaee thi."
3100,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere ghar, meri baari ke din, mere halaq aur seeney ke darmyan tek lagaey huey wafat paaii, Allah Taala ne (wafaat ke waqt) mere thook aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke thook ko aik sath jama kar diya tha, bayan kya (wo is tarah ke) Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu)) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke bhai ( miswak liye huey andar aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey chabaa na sakey. isliye maine usey apne hath mein ley liya aur maine usey chabaaney ke baad wo miswak aap ke daanton par malii."
3101,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein milney ke liye hazir huin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey ka masjid mein aetikaf kiye huey they. phir wo wapas honey ke liye uthein to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unke sath uthey . jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni paak bevi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke darwaza ke qareeb pahunchey jo masjide-Nabawi ke darwazey se mila hua tha to 2 Ansari sahabi ( Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) aur Ibaad-bin-Bishr (Raziallahu anhu)) wahan se guzrey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unhon-ne salam kya aur aagey badhney lagey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya, zara thahar jao (mere sath meri biwi Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) hain yani koi doosra nahi ( un donon ne arz kya. sub'haan-Allaah, ya Rasulullah! un hazraat par aap ka ye farmana bada sakht guzraa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke shaitan insan ke andar is tarah daudta rehta hai jaisey jism mein khoon daudta hai. mujhey yahi khatrah hua ke kahin tumharey dilon mein bhi koi waswasa paida na ho jaey."
3102,"main ( Ummul-Momenin ( Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar ke uper chadhaa, to dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) kar rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peeth qible ki taraf thi aur chehra Mubarak Sham (Syria) ki taraf tha."
3103,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Asr ki Namaz padhtey to dhoop abhi unke hujrey mein baqi rehti thi.
3104,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba detey huey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ki taraf ishara kya aur farmaya ke usi taraf se (yani mashriq ki taraf se) fitney barpa hongey, teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah farmaya ke yahin se shaitan ka sar namudaar hoga."
3105,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ghar mein maujood they. achcha unhon-ne suna ke koi sahib Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein andar aaney ki ijazat maang rahe hain. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke) maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap dekhtey nahi, ye shakhs ghar mein janey ki ijazat maang raha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke mera khayal hai ye falan sahib hain, Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik chacha ! razaat bhi un tamam chizon ko haram kar deti hai jinhein paidaaish haram karti hai."
3106,"jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa huey to unhon-ne unko (yani Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko) Bahrain (aamil bana kar) bheja aur aik parwaana likh kar unko diya aur is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki anguthi ki mehar lagaaii, mehar par teen linein khudii hui thin, aik line mein ''Muhammad'' dusri mein '' rasool'' teesri mein ''Allaah'' khuda hua tha."
3107,"Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein 2 puraaney jootey nikal kar dikhaaey jin mein 2 tasmey lagey huey they, iske baad phir Sabit Bunani ne mujh se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke wo donon jootey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke they."
3108,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne hamein aik pewand lagi hui chadar nikal kar dikhai aur batlaya ke isi kapdey main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Rooh qabz hui thi aur Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne Humaid se bayan kya, unhon-ne abu-Barda se itna zyada bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Yaman ki bani hui aik motii izaar ( tahmad (aur aik kambal unhiin kambalon mein se jinko tum malba (aur mota pewand daar kehtey ho ( hamein nikal kar dikhai ."
3109,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka pani peeney ka piyala toot gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tootii hui jaghon ko chandi ki zanjeeron se judwaa liya. Aasim kehtey hain ke maine wo piyala dekha hai. aur is mein maine pani bhi piyaa hai.
3110,"jab ham sab hazraat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ke baad Yazeed-bin-Muaawiya ke yahan se Madina Munawra tashrif laey to Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se mulaqat ki, aur kaha agar aapko koi zarurat ho to mujhey hukm farma dijiye. (Zainul-Aabedeen ne bayan kya ke) maine kaha, mujhey koi zarurat nahi hai. phir Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha to kya aap mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki talwaar inayat farmaaengey? kyonke mujhey khof hai ke kuchh log (banu-Umayya) usey aap se na chheen lein aur Allah ki qism ! agar wo talwaar aap mujhey inayat farma dein to koi shakhs bhi jab tak meri jaan baqi hai usey chheen nahi sakega. phir Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik qissa bayan kya ke Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ki maujoodgii mein abu-Jahal ki aik beti ( jameela naam ke (Raziallahu anhu)) ko paigham nikah de diya tha. maine khud suna ke isi mas'ale par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne isi member par khadey ho kar sahaba ko khitab farmaya, mein us waqt baligh tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutbe mein farmaya ke Fatima mujh se hai. aur mujhey dar hai ke kahin wo (is rishta ki wjah se) kisi gunah mein na pad jaey ke apne Deen mein wo kisi fitne mein mubtala ho. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khandan banii-abd-Shams ke aik apne daamaad ( Aas bin Rabe (ka zikr kya aur daamaadii se mutaalliq aap ne unki tareef ki, aap ne farmaya ke unhon-ne mujh se jo baat kahi sach kahii, jo wada kya, usey pura kya. main kisi halal (yani nikah saanii) ko haram nahi kar sakta aur na kisi haram ko halal banata hun. lekin Allah ki qasam! Rasulullah ki beti aur Allah ke dushman ki beti aik sath jama nahi hoongii."
3111,"agar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura kehney waley hotey to us din hotey jab kuchh log Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke aamilon ki (jo zakat wsool kartey they) shikayat karne unke paas aaey. unhon-ne mujh se kaha Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ja aur ye zakat ka parwaana ley jaa. unse kehna ke ye parwaana Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka likhwaayaa hua hai. tum apne aamilon ko hukm 2 ke wo usi ke mutabiq amal karein. chunanche main usey lekar Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unhein paigham pahuncha diya, lekin unhon-ne farmaya ke hamein uski koi zarurat nahi (kyonke hamarey paas uski naql maujood hai) maine ja kar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se ye waqia bayan kya, to unhon-ne farmaya ke achchha, phir us parwaaney ko jahan se uthaya hai wahin rakh do."
3112,"mere walid ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ne mujh ko kaha ke ye parwaana Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko ley ja kar de aao, usmein zakat se mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bayan ki hui ehkaamaat darj hain."
3113,"Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko chuki peesney ki bahut takleef hoti. phir unhein malum hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh qaidi aaey hain. isliye wo bhi unmein se aik londi ya ghulam ki darkhaast lekar hazir huin. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maujood nahi they. wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se iske mutaalliq keh kar) wapas ( chali aaein . phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney unki darkhaast pesh kar di. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke usey sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey yahan (raat hi ko) tashrif laey. jab ham apne bistaron par let chukey they (jab ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha (to ham log khadey honey lagey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis tarah ho waisey hi letey raho. (phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke beech mein baith gaey aur itney qareeb ho gaey ke) maine aap ke donon qadmon ki thandak apne seeney par paaii. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo kuchh tum logon ne (laundii ya ghulaam) maangey hain, main tumhen us se behtar baat kyon na bataaoon, jab tum donon apne bistar par let jao (to soney se pahley) Allahu-akbar 34 martaba aur al-Hamdulillah 33 martaba aur Subhan-Allah 33 martaba padh liya karo, ye amal behtar hai us se jo tum donon ne maanga hai."
3114,"ham ansaariyon ke qabeele mein aik Ansari ke ghar bachcha paida ho to unhon-ne bachchey ka naam Muhammad rakhney ka irada kya aur Shoba ne Mansoor se riwayat karke bayan kya hai ke un Ansari ne bayan kya (jinke yahan bachcha paida hua tha) ke main bachchey ko apni gardan par utha kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Sulaiman ki riwayat mein hai ke unke yahan bachcha paida hua, to unhon-ne uska naam Muhammad rakhna chaha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke mere naam par naam rakho, lekin meri kunniyat ( abul-Qaasim ( par kunniyat na rakhna , kyonke mujhey taqseem karne wala ( Qasim ( banaya gaya hai. main tum mein taqseem karta hun, aur Husain ne (apni riwayat mein) yun bayan kya, ke mujhey taqseem karne wala ( Qasim ( bana kar bheja gaya hai, main tum mein taqseem karta hun. Amr-bin-Marzooq ne kaha ke hamein Shoba ne khabar di, unse Qatada ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Salim se suna unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se ke un Ansari sahabi ne apne bachchey ka naam Qasim rakhna chaha tha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere naam par naam rakho lekin kunniyat na rakho."
3115,"hamarey qabeele mein aik shakhs ke yahan bachcha paida hua, to unhon-ne uska naam Qasim rakha , Ansar kehney lagey ke ham tumhen abul-Qaasim keh kar kabhi nahi pukaarengey aur ham tumhari aankh thandii nahi karengey ye sun kar wo Ansari Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! mere ghar aik bachcha paida hua hai. maine uska naam Qasim rakha hai to Ansar kehtey hain ham teri kunniyat abul-Qaasim nahi pukaarengey aur teri aankh thandii nahi karengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ansaar ne theek kaha hai mere naam par naam rakho, lekin meri kunniyat mat rakho, kyonke Qasim main hon.''"
3116,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jiske sath Allah Taala bhalai chahta hai usey Deen ki samajh de deta hai. aur dene wala to Allah hi hai main to sirf taqseem karne wala hun aur apne dushmanon ke muqaabley mein ye ummat (muslima) hamesha ghalib rahegi . yahan tak ke Allah ka hukm (qiyamat ( aa jaey aur us waqt bhi wo ghalib hi hongey.''
3117,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''na main tumhen koi cheez deta hun, na tum se kisi cheez ko roktaa hun. main to sirf taqseem karne wala hun. jahan jahaan ka mujhey hukm hota hai bas wahin rakh deta hoon.''"
3118,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they kuchh log Allah Taala ke maal ko be-jaa udaatey hain, unhein qiyamat ke din aag milegii."
3119,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ghodon ki peshaaniyon se qiyamat tak khair w barkat ( aakhirat mein) aur ghaneemat ( duniya mein) bandhi hui hai.''
3120,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab Kisraa mar jaeyga to uske baad koi Kisraa paida na hoga aur jab qaisar mar jaeyga to uski baad koi qaisar paida na hoga aur us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, tum log un donon ke khazaaney Allah ke rastey mein kharch karogey.''"
3121,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab Kisraa mar jaeyga to uske baad koi Kisraa paida na hoga aur jab qaisar mar jaeyga to uski baad koi qaisar paida na hoga aur us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, tum log un donon ke khazaaney Allah ke rastey mein kharch karogey.''"
3122,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya '' mere liye (muraad ummat hai) ghaneemat ke maal halal kiye gaey hain.''
3123,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo Allah ke rastey mein jihad karey, jihad hi ki niyat se nikley, Allah ke kalam (uske waadey ( ko sach jaan kar, to Allah uska zaamin hai. ya to Allah Taala usko Shahid karke jannat mein ley jaeyga ya usko sawab aur ghaneemat ka maal dila kar uske ghar lota laaeyga.''"
3124,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''banii-Israaeel ke paighambaron mein se aik Nabi (Yoosha' (Alaihissalam) ( ne jang karne ka irada kya to apni qaum se kaha ke mere sath koi aisa shakhs jisne abhi nai shadi ki ho aur biwi ke sath raat bhi na guzari ho aur wo raat guzaarnaa chahta ho aur wo shakhs jisne ghar banaya ho aur abhi uski chhat na rakhi ho aur wo shakhs jisne haamla bakri ya haamla oontniyan kharidi hon aur usey unke bachchey janne ka intizar ho to (aisey logon mein se koi bhi) hamarey sath jihad mein na chaley. phir unhon-ne jihad kya, aur jab us aabadi (Areehaa) se qareeb huey to Asr ka waqt ho gaya ya iske qareeb waqt hua. unhon-ne suraj se farmaya ke to bhi Allah ka taabe'-farmaan hai aur main bhi uska taabe'-farmaan hun. aey Allah ! hamarey liye usey apni jagah par rok de. chunanche suraj ruk gaya, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne unhein fateh inayat farmai . phir unhon-ne ghaneemat ke maalon ko jama kya aur aag usey jalaaney ke liye aai lekin jalaa na sakii, us Nabi ne farmaya ke tum mein se kisi ne maale-ghanimat mein chori ki hai. isliye har qabeele ka aik aadmi aa kar mere hath par bait karey (jab bait karne lagey to) aik qabeele ke shakhs ka hath unke hath se chimat gaya. unhon-ne farmaya, ke chori tumharey qabeele hi walon ne ki hai. ab tumharey qabeeley ke sab log aaein aur bait karein. chunanche us qabeeley ke do-teen aadmiyon ka hath is tarah unke hath se chimat gaya, to aap ne farmaya ke chori tumhen logon ne ki hai. (aakhir chori maan li gai) aur wo log gaaey ke sar ki tarah soney ka aik sar laey (jo ghaneemat mein se churaa liya gaya tha) aur usey maale-ghanimat mein rakh diya, tab aag aai aur usey jalaa gaee, phir ghaneemat Allah Taala ne hamarey liye jaaiz qarar de di, hamari kamzori aur aajizii ko dekha. isliye hamarey waastey halal qarar de di."
3125,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ''agar musalmanon ki aaney wali naslon ka khayal na hota to jo Shahar bhi fateh hota mein usey faatihon mein isi tarah taqseem kar diya karta jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki taqseem ki thii.''
3126,"ham se abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aik dehati ( laahiq bin zameera Bahili ( ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha aik shakhs hai jo ghaneemat hasil karne ke liye jihad mein Sharik hua, aik shakhs hai jo isliye shirkat karta hai ke uski bahaadurii ke charchey zabanon par aa jaaein, aik shakhs isliye ladtaa hai ke uski dhaak baith jaey, to unmein se Allah ke rastey mein kon sa hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs jang mein shirkat isliye karey taake Allah ka kalima (deen) hi buland rahe. faqat wahi Allah ke rastey mein hai."
3127,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein deebaa ki kuchh chaadarein tohfe ke taur par aai thin. jin mein soney ki ghundiyaan lagi hui thin, unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne chand ashaab mein taqseem farma diya aur aik chadar Makhrima bin Nofal (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye rakh li. phir Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur unke sath unke sahibzadey Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aap darwazey par khadey ho gaey aur kaha ke mera naam lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bula la . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki awaz suni to chadar lekar bahar tashrif laey aur uski ghundiyaan unke samney kar dein. phir farmaya : Abu-Miswar ! ye Quba maine tumharey liye chipa kar rakh li thi. Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) zara tez tabeeat ke aadmi they. ibne-Ulaih ne Ayub ke waastey se ye hadis (mursalan hi) riwayat ki hai. aur Haatim-bin-Wardaan ne bayan kya ke ham se Ayub ne bayan kya, unse ibne-abi-Mulaika ne unse Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan kuchh qubaaein aaiin thin, is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Leis ne ibne-abi-Mulaika se ki hai."
3128,sahaba ( Ansar ( kuchh khajoor ke darakht Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bataur tohfa de diya kartey they lekin jab Allah Taala ne banu-Quraiza aur banu-Nazeer ke qabaayel par fateh di to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske baad is tarah ke hadiye wapas farma diya kartey they.
3129,"unse Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jamal ki jang ke mauqe par jab Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey to mujhey bulaya. main unke pahlu mein ja kar khada ho gaya, unhon-ne kaha betey ! aaj ki ladai mein zaalim maara jaeyga ya mazloom? main samajhta hun ke aaj main mazloom qatl kya jaaunga aur mujhey sabse zyada fikr apne qarzon ki hai. kya tumhen bhi kuchh andaza hai ke qarz ada karne ke baad hamara kuchh maal bach sakega? phir unhon-ne kaha betey ! hamara maal farokht karke us se qarz ada kar dena. iske baad unhon-ne aik tehai ki mere liye aur us tehai ke teesrey hisse ki wasiiyat mere bachchon ke liye ki, yani Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke bachchon ke liye. unhon-ne farmaya tha ke us tehai ke teen hissey kar lena aur agar qarz ki adaaeygi ke baad hamarey amwaal mein se kuchh bach jaey to uska aik tehai tumharey bachchon ke liye hoga. Hisham rawi ne bayan kya ke Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke kuchh ladkey Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke ladkon ke ham-umr they. jaisey Khubaib aur Ibad aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke us waqt nau (9) ladkey aur nau (9) ladkiyan thin. Abdullah-bin-Zubair ne bayan kya ke phir Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) mujhey apne qarz ke silsiley mein wasiiyat karne lagey aur farmaney lagey ke betaa! agar qarz ada karne se aajiz ho jao to mere Malik w Maula se usmein madad chaahanaa. Abdullah ne bayan kya ke qism Allah ki! main unki baat na samajh sakaa, maine puchha ke baabaa aap ke Maula kon hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke Allah paak! Abdullah ne bayan kya, qism Allah ki ! qarz ada karne mein jo bhi dushwari samney aai to maine isi tarah dua ki, ke aey Zuber ke maulaa! unki taraf se unka qarz ada kara de aur adaaeygi ki sura paida ho jati thi. chunanche jab Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) (usi mauqe par) Shahid ho gaey to unhon-ne tarke mein dirham w Dinar nahi chhodey balke unka tarka kuchh to araazii ki sura mein tha aur usi mein Ghaaba ki zameen bhi shamil thi. gyara (11) makanon Madina mein they, 2 makan Basra mein they, aik makan Kufa mein tha aur aik misr mein tha. Abdullah ne bayan kya ke un par jo itna Sara qarz ho gaya tha uski sura ye hui thi ke jab unke paas koi shakhs apna maal lekar amanat rakhney aata to aap usey kehtey ke nahi albatta is sura mein rakh sakta hun ke ye mere zimmey bataur qarz rahe. kyonke mujhey iske zaaye ho janey ka bhi khof hai. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) kisi ilaaqey ke ameer kabhi nahi baney they. na wo khiraaj wsool karne par kabhi muqarrar huey aur na koi doosra ohda unhon-ne qabool kya, albatta unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saat"
3130,"Usman (Raziallahu anhu) badr ki ladai mein Sharik na ho sakey they. unke nikah main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sahibzadi thin aur wo bimar thin. unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen bhi itna hi sawab milega jitna badr mein Sharik hone-waale kisi shakhs ko , aur itna hi hissey bhi milega."
3131,"jab Hawazin ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur apne maalon aur qaidiyon ki waapsii ka sawal kya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sachchii baat mujhey sabse zyada pasand hai. in donon chizon mein se tum aik hi wapas ley saktey ho. apne qaidi wapas ley lo ya phir maal ley lo, aur maine tumhara intizar bhi kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne taqriban das din tak Taaif se waapsii par unka intizar kya aur jab ye baat un par waazeh ho gaee ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki sirf aik hi cheez ( qaidi ya maal ( wapas kar saktey hain to unhon-ne kaha ke ham apne qaidi hi wapas lena chahtey hain. ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko khitab farmaya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki shaan ke mutabiq hamd w sana karne ke baad farmaya ''ammaa ba'd! tumharey ye bhai ab hamarey paas tauba karke aaey hain aur main munasib samajhta hun ke unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. isi liye jo shakhs apni khushi se ghaneemat ke apne hissey ke (qaidii) wapas karna chahey wo kar de aur jo shakhs chahta ho ke iska hissey baqi rahe aur hamein jab iske baad sabse pehli ghaneemat miley to usmein se iske hissey ki adaaeygi kar di jaey to wo bhi apne qaidi wapas kar de, (aur jab hamein doosrey ghaneemat milegii to uska hissey ada kar diya jaaeyga).'' is par sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ham apni khushi se unhein apne hissey wapas kar detey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''lekin hamein ye malum na ho saka ke kin logon ne apni khushi se ijazat di aur kin logon ne nahi di hai. isliye sab log (apne khemon mein) wapas chaley jayen aur tumharey sardaar log tumhari baat hamarey samney aa kar bayan karein.'' sab log wapas chaley gaey aur unke sardaaron ne us masla par guftgu ki aur phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aa kar khabar di ke sab log khushi se ijazat detey hain. yahi wo khabar hai jo Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke silsiley mein hamein malum hui hai."
3132,"jab Hawazin ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur apne maalon aur qaidiyon ki waapsii ka sawal kya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sachchii baat mujhey sabse zyada pasand hai. in donon chizon mein se tum aik hi wapas ley saktey ho. apne qaidi wapas ley lo ya phir maal ley lo, aur maine tumhara intizar bhi kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne taqriban das din tak Taaif se waapsii par unka intizar kya aur jab ye baat un par waazeh ho gaee ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki sirf aik hi cheez ( qaidi ya maal ( wapas kar saktey hain to unhon-ne kaha ke ham apne qaidi hi wapas lena chahtey hain. ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko khitab farmaya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah ki shaan ke mutabiq hamd w sana karne ke baad farmaya ''ammaa ba'd! tumharey ye bhai ab hamarey paas tauba karke aaey hain aur main munasib samajhta hun ke unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. isi liye jo shakhs apni khushi se ghaneemat ke apne hissey ke (qaidii) wapas karna chahey wo kar de aur jo shakhs chahta ho ke iska hissey baqi rahe aur hamein jab iske baad sabse pehli ghaneemat miley to usmein se iske hissey ki adaaeygi kar di jaey to wo bhi apne qaidi wapas kar de, (aur jab hamein doosrey ghaneemat milegii to uska hissey ada kar diya jaaeyga).'' is par sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ham apni khushi se unhein apne hissey wapas kar detey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''lekin hamein ye malum na ho saka ke kin logon ne apni khushi se ijazat di aur kin logon ne nahi di hai. isliye sab log (apne khemon mein) wapas chaley jayen aur tumharey sardaar log tumhari baat hamarey samney aa kar bayan karein.'' sab log wapas chaley gaey aur unke sardaaron ne us masla par guftgu ki aur phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aa kar khabar di ke sab log khushi se ijazat detey hain. yahi wo khabar hai jo Hawazin ke qaidiyon ke silsiley mein hamein malum hui hai."
3133,"ham abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein hazir they ( khana laya gaya aur) wahan murghi ka zikr honey laga. bani Tameem Allah ke aik aadmi surkh rang waley wahan maujood they. ghaaliban aazad kiye hue ghulaamon mein se they. unhein bhi abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne khaney par bulaya , wo kehney lagey ke maine murghi ko gandii cheezein khaatey aik martaba dekha tha to mujhey badi nafrat hui aur maine qism kha li ke ab kabhi murghi ka gosht na khaaunga. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qareeb aa jao (tumhaarii qism par) main tum se aik hadis usi silsiley ki bayan karta hun, qabila ash'ar ke chand logon ko sath lekar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main (jange-Tabook ke liye) hazir hua aur sawari ki darkhaast ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ki qasam! main tumharey liye sawari ka intizam nahi kar sakta, kyonke mere paas koi aisi cheez nahi hai jo tumhari sawari ke kaam aa sakey.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ghaneemat ke kuchh oont aaey, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey mutaalliq malum farmaya, aur farmaya ke qabila ash'ar ke log kahan hain? chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne panch oont hamein diye janey ka hukm saadir farmaya, khub motey-taazey aur farba. jab ham chalney lagey to ham ne aapas mein kaha ke jo naa-munaasib tariqa ham ne ikhtiyar kya us se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us Atiya mein hamarey liye koi barkat nahi ho saktii. chunanche ham phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke ham ne pahley jab aap se darkhaast ki thi to aap ne qism kha kar farmaya tha ke main tumhari sawari ka intizam nahi kar sakoonga. shayad aapko wo qism yad na rahi ho, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumhari sawari ka intizam waqei nahi kya, wo Allah Taala hai jisne tumhen ye sawaariyaan de di hain. Allah ki qism ! tum is par yaqin rakho ke inshaAllah jab bhi mein koi qism khaaun , phir mujh par ye baat zahir ho jaey ke behtar aur munasib tarze-amal iske siwa mein hai to main wahi karunga jis mein achai hogi aur qism ka kaffara de doonga."
3134,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf aik lashkar rawaana kya. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi lashkar ke sath they. ghaneemat ke taur par oonton ki aik badi tadaad us lashkar ko milii. isliye iske har sipaahii ko hisse mein bhi baara baara gyara (11) gyara oont miley they aur eik-eik oont aur inaam mein mila.
3135,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuchh muhimon ke mauqe par usmein Sharik honey walon ko ghaneemat ke aam hisson ke ilawa (khums wghaira mein se) apne taur par bhi diya kartey they.
3136,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hijrat ki khabar hamein milii, to ham Yaman mein they. isliye ham bhi aap ki khidmat mein muhajir ki haisiyat se hazir honey ke liye rawaana huey. main tha, mere bhai they. (meri umr un donon se kam thi, donon bhaiyon mein) aik abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) they aur doosrey abu-Raham. ya unhon-ne ye kaha ke apni qaum ke chand afraad ke sath ya ye kaha tirpan ya baawan aadmiyon ke sath (ye log rawaana huey they) ham kashtii mein sawar huey to hamari kashtii Najashi ke mulk Habsha pahunch gaee aur wahan hamein Jafar bin abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) apne doosrey sathiyon ke sath miley. Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein yahan bheja tha aur hukm diya tha ke ham yahin rahen. chunanche ham bhi wahin thahar gaey aur phir sab aik sath (Madeena) hazir huey, jab ham khidmat nabwi mein pahunchey, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar fateh kar chukey they. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (doosrey mujaahidon ke saath) hamara bhi hissey maale-ghanimat mein lagaya. ya unhon-ne ye kaha ke aap ne ghaneemat mein se hamein bhi ata farmaya, halanke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi aisey shakhs ka ghaneemat mein hissey nahi lagaya jo ladai mein Sharik na raha ho. sirf unhi logon ko hissey mila tha, jo ladai mein Sharik they. albatta hamarey kashtii ke sathiyon aur Jafar aur unke sathiyon ko bhi aap ne ghaneemat mein Sharik kya tha (halanke ham log ladai mein Sharik nahi huey they)."
3137,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jab Bahrain se wsool ho kar mere paas maal aayega to main tumhen is-is tarah aur is tarah (teen lap ( doonga iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur Bahrain ka maal us waqt tak na aaya. phir jab wahan se maal aaya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke hukm se manaadii ne elaan kya ke jiska bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par koi qarz ho ya aap ka koi wada ho to hamarey paas aaey. mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein gaya aur arz kya ke mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha. chunanche unhon-ne teen lap bhar kar mujhey diya. Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne apne donon hathon se ishara karke ( lap bharney ki) kaifiyat batai phir ham se Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke ibne-Munkadir ne bhi ham se isi tarah bayan kya tha aur aik martaba Sufiyan ne (pichhli sanad ke saath) bayan kya ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne mujhey kuchh nahi diya. phir main hazir hua, aur is martaba bhi mujhey unhon-ne kuchh nahi diya. phir main teesri martaba hazir hua aur arz kya ke maine aik martaba aap se maanga aur aap ne inayat nahi farmaya, dobara maanga , phir bhi aap ne inayat nahi farmaya aur phir maanga lekin aap ne inayat nahi farmaya, ab ya aap mujhey dijiye ya phir mere barey mein kanjoosii se kaam liijiye, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke tum kehtey ho ke mere mamley mein kanjoosii se kaam leta hai. halanke tumhen deney se jab bhi maine munh phera to mere dil mein ye baat hoti thi ke tumhen kabhi na kabhi dena zaroor hai. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke ham se Amr ne bayan kya, unse Muhammad-bin Ali ne aur unse Jaabir ne, phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey aik lap bhar kar diya aur farmaya ke usey shumaar kar maine shumaar kya to panch so ki tadaad thi, iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke itna hi 2 martaba aur ley-ley. aur ibne-munkadir ne bayan kya (ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya tha) kanjoosii se zyada badtareen aur kya bimari ho sakti hai."
3138,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maqam Jaarana mein ghaneemat taqseem kar rahe they ke aik shakhs zul-khuwesra ne aap se kaha, insaf se kaam lijiye , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar main bhi insaf se kaam na loon to bad-bakht hua.''"
3139,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ke qaidiyon ke barey mein farmaya tha ke agar mut'im-bin-adii (jo kufr ki haalat mein mar gaey they) zinda hotey aur in naapaak, napak logon ki sifarish kartey to main unki sifarish se inhein (fidya liye baghair) chhod detaa."
3140,"main aur Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah! aap ne banu-Muttalib ko to inayat farmaya lekin ham ko chhod diya, halanke ham ko aap se wahi rishta hai jo banu-Muttalib ko aap se hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke banu-Muttalib aur banu-Haashim aik hi hai. Leis ne bayan kya ke mujh se Yunus ne bayan kya aur (is riwayat mein) ye zyadti ki ke Juber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Abd-Shams aur banu-Naufal ko nahi diya tha, aur ibne-Ishaq (saahib maghaazii) ne kaha hai ke Abd-Shams, Hashim aur muttalib aik maan se they aur unki maan ka naam Aatika-bin-Murra tha aur Nofal bap ki taraf se unke bhai they (unki maan dusri thiin)."
3141,"badr ki ladai mein, main saf ke sath khada hua tha. maine jo daain-baaiin taraf dekha, to mere donon taraf qabila Ansar ke 2 nau-umr ladkey they. maine aarzoo ki kash! mein unse zabardast zyada umr walon ke beech mein hota. aik ne meri taraf ishara kya, aur puchha chacha ! aap abu-Jahal ko bhi pehchantey hain? maine kaha ke haan! lekin betey tum logon ko us se kya kaam hai? ladkey ne jawab diya mujhey malum hua hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gaaliyaan deta hai, us zaat ki qism ! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar mujhey wo mil gaya to us waqt tak mein us se juda na hunga jab tak ham mein se koi jiski qismat mein pahley marnaa hoga, mar na jaey, mujhey is par badi hairat hui. phir doosrey ne ishara kya aur wahi baatein usne bhi kahiin. abhi chand minute hi guzrey they ke mujhey abu-Jahal dikhai diya jo logon mein (kuffaar ke lashkar mein) ghoomtaa phir raha tha. maine un ladkon se kaha ke jiske mutaalliq tum log mujh se poochh rahe they, wo samney ( phirtaa hua nazar aa raha ( hai. donon ne apni talwaarein sanbhaaliin aur is par jhapat padey aur hamla karke usey qatl kar dala. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aapko khabar di, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke tum donon mein se kis ne usey maara hai? donon naujawaanon ne kaha ke maine qatl kya hai. isliye aap ne unse puchha ke kya apni talwaarein tum ne saaf kar li hain? unhon-ne arz kya ke nahi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon talwaaron ko dekha aur farmaya ke tum donon hi ne usey maara hai. aur uska saman Muaaz-bin-Amr-bin-Jamooa' ko milega. wo donon naujawaan Muaaz-bin-Ifraa aur Muaaz-bin-Amr-bin-Jamooa' they Muhammad ne kaha Yusuf ne Saleh se suna aur Ibrahim ne apne bap se suna."
3142,"jange-Hunain ke saal ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey. phir jab hamara dushman se saamnaa hua to ( shuruaat mein) Islami lashkar haarney laga. itney mein maine dekha ke mushrekeen ke lashkar ka aik shakhs aik musalman ke uper chadhaa hua hai. isliye main fauran hi ghoom padaa aur uske peechhey se aa kar talwaar uski gardan par maarii. ab wo shakhs mujh par toot padaa, aur mujhey itni zor se us ne bheencha ke meri Rooh jaisey qabz honey ko thi. aakhir jab usko maut ne aa dabochaa, tab kahin ja kar usne mujhey chhodaa. iske baad mujhey Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) miley, to maine unse puchha ke musalman ab kis haalat mein hain? unhon-ne kaha ke jo Allah ka hukm tha wahi hua. lekin musalman haarney ke baad phir muqable par sanbhal gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith gaey aur farmaya ke jisne bhi kisi kaafir ko qatl kya ho aur is par wo gawah bhi pesh kar de to maqtool ka Sara saaz w saman usey hi milega ( abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( mein bhi khada hua aur maine kaha ke meri taraf se kon gawahi dega ? lekin (jab meri taraf se koi na utha to ( mein baith gaya. phir dobara Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) aaj ( jisne kisi kaafir ko qatl kya aur is par uski taraf se koi gawah bhi ho to maqtool ka Sara saman usey milega. is martaba phir maine khadey ho kar kaha ke meri taraf se kon gawahi dega ? aur phir mujhey baithna padaa. teesri martaba phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahi irshad dohraya aur us martaba jab main khada hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud hi malum farmaya, kis cheez ke mutaalliq keh rahe ho abu-Qataada! maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Sara waqia bayan kar diya, to aik sahib ( Aswad bin Khuzai Aslamii) ne bataya ke abu-Qatada sach kehtey hain, ya Rasulullah ! aur us maqtool ka saman mere paas mehfooz hai. aur mere haq mein unhein razi kar dijiye (ke wo maqtool ka saman mujh se na lein) lekin Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke nahi Allah ki qism ! Allah ke aik sher ke saath, jo Allah aur uske rasool ke liye ladey , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisa nahi karengey ke unka saman tumhen de dein, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar ne sach kaha hai. phir aap ne saman abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ko ata farmaya, abu-Qatada ne kaha ke phir uski zirah bech kar maine bani Salma mein aik baagh khareed liya aur ye pahlaa maal tha jo Islam laney ke baad maine hasil kya tha."
3143,"Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh rupya maanga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ata farmaya, phir dobara maine maanga aur us martaba bhi aap ne ata farmaya, phir irshad farmaya, hakeem ! ye maal dekhney mein sar-sabz bahut meethaa aur mazedaar hai lekin jo shakhs usey dil ki be-gharzii ke sath ley uske maal main to barkat hoti hai aur jo shakhs isey laalach aur hirs ke sath ley to uske maal mein barkat nahi hoti, balke uski misal us shakhs jaisi hai jo khaaey jata hai lekin uska pet nahi bharta aur uper ka hath (dene wala) nichey ke hath ( leney waale) se behtar hota hai. Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ke baad ab main kisi se kuchh bhi nahi maangonga, yahan tak ke us duniya mein se chala jaaunga. chunanche (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) unhein dene ke liye bulaatey, lekin wo usmein se aik paisaa bhi leney se inkar kar detey. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) (apne zamana khilafat mein) unhein dene ke liye bulatey aur unse bhi leney se unhon-ne inkar kar diya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke musalmaanon! main unhein unka haq deta hun jo Allah Taala ne faiy ke maal se unka hissey muqarrar kya hai. lekin ye usey bhi qabool nahi kartey. Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ho gaee lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad unhon-ne kisi se koi cheez nahi li."
3144,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! zamana jahiliyat ( kufr ( mein maine aik din ke aetikaf ki mannat maana thi, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey pura karne ka hukm farmaya, Naafe ne bayan kya ke Hunain ke qaidiyon mein se umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko 2 baandiyaan mili thin. to aap ne unhein Makka ke kisi ghar mein rakha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hunain ke qaidiyon par ehsan kya (aur sab ko muft aazad kar diyaa) to galiyon mein wo daudney lagey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Abdullaah! dekho to ye kya mamla hai. unhon-ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un par ehsan kya hai (aur Hunain ke tamam qaidi muft aazad kar diye gaey hain) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir ja un donon ladkiyon ko bhi aazad kar de. Naafe ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maqam Jaarana se Umre ka ehram nahi baandha tha. agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se Umre ka ehram baandhtey to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye zaroor malum hota aur Jareer-bin-Haazim ne jo Ayub se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, usmein yun hai ke (wo donon baandiyaan jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko mili thiin) khums mein se thin. (aitikaaf se mutaalliq ye riwaayat) Mamar ne Ayub se naql ki hai, unse Naafe ne, unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne nazar ka qissa jo riwayat kya hai is mein aik din ka lafz nahi hai."
3145,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko diya aur kuchh logon ko nahi diya. ghaaliban jin logon ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi diya tha, unko na-gawar hua. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main kuchh aisey logon ko deta hun ke mujhey jinke bigad janey (Islam se phir janey (aur be-sabrii ka dar hai. aur kuchh log aisey hain jin par main bharosa karta hun, Allah Taala ne unke dilon mein bhalai aur be niyaazii rakhi hai (unko mein nahi detaa) Amr bin taghlab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unhiin mein shamil hain. Amr bin taghlab (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri nisbat ye jo kalima farmaya agar iske badley surkh oont miltey to bhi mein itna khush na hota. abu-Aasim ne Jarir se bayan kya ke maine Hasan Basri se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke ham se Amr bin taghlab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas maal ya qaidi aaey they aur unhiin ko aap ne taqseem farmaya tha."
3146,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Quraish ko main unka dil milaaney ke liye deta hun, kyonke unki jahiliyat ( kufr (ka zamana abhi taaza guzra hai (unki diljoii karna zaroori hai).''"
3147,"jab Allah Taala ne apne rasool ko qabila Hawazin ke maalon mein se ghaneemat di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quraish ke kuchh aadmiyon ko (dilon ko parchaaney se) so-so oont dene lagey to kuchh Ansari logon ne kaha Allah Taala Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bakhshish kare. aap Quraish ko to de rahe hain aur hamein chhod diya. halanke unka khoon abhi tak hamari talwaaron se tapak raha hai. ( Quraish ke logon ko haal hi mein ham ne maara , unke Shahar ko ham hi ne fateh kya ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab ye khabar pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ko bulaya aur unhein chamdey ke aik derey mein jama kya, unke siwa kisi doosrey sahabi ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi bulaya. jab sab Ansari log jama ho gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif laey aur malum farmaya ke aap logon ke barey mein jo baat mujhey malum hui wo kahan tak sahi hai? Ansar ke samajh daar logon ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham mein jo aql waley hain, wo to koi aisi baat zaban par nahi laey hain, haan chand nau-umr ladkey hain, unhon-ne ye kaha hai ke Allah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bakhshish karey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quraish ko to de rahe hain aur ham ko nahi detey halanke hamari talwaaron se abhi tak unke khoon tapak rahe hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main kuchh aisey logon ko deta hun jinka kufr ka zamana abhi guzra hai. (aur unko de kar unka dil milaataa hun) kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke jab doosrey log maal w daulat lekar wapas ja rahe hongey, to tum log apne gharon ko Rasulullah ko lekar wapas ja rahe hogey. Allah ki qasam! tumharey sath jo kuchh wapas ja raha hai wo us se behtar hai jo doosrey log apne sath wapas ley jaengey. sab ansaariyon ne kaha : beshak ya Rasulullah! ham is par razi aur khush hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ''mere baad tum ye dekhogey ke tum par doosrey logon ko muqaddam kya jaeyga us waqt tum sabr karnaa, (dangaa fasaad na karnaa) yahan tak ke Allah Taala se ja milo aur uske rasool se hauze-kausar par.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, phir ham se sabr na ho saka."
3148,"mere bap Muhammad-bin-Jubair ne kaha aur unhein Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. aap ke sath aur bhi sahaba they. Hunain ke jihad se waapsii ho rahi thi. rastey mein kuchh baddoo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se lipat gaey (loot ka maal) aap se maangtey they. wo aap se aisa liptey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik babool ke darakht ki taraf dhakel ley gaey. aap ki chadar usmein atak kar reh gaee. us waqt aap thahar gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' (bhaaiyo) meri chadar to de do. agar mere paas un kaantey daar darakhton ki tadaad mein oont hotey to wo bhi tum mein taqseem kar detaa. tum mujhey kanjoos, jhoota aur buzdil hargiz nahi paaogey.''"
3149,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ja raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Najran ki bani hui chaudey haashiya ki aik chadar odhey huey they. itney mein aik dehati ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gher liya aur zor se aapko kheenchaa, maine aap ke shaaney ko dekha, is par chadar ke koney ka nishan pad gaya, aisa kheenchaa. phir kehney laga. Allah ka maal jo aap ke paas hai is mein se kuchh mujh ko dilaaiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf dekha aur hans diye. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey dene ka hukm farmaya."
3150,"Hunain ki ladai ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ghaneemat ki) taqseem mein kuchh logon ko zyada diya. jaisey Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) ko so oont diye, itney hi oont Uena-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko diye aur kai Arab ke ashraaf logon ko isi tarah taqseem mein zyada diya. is par aik shakhs (mau'tab bin-Qushair munafiq ( ne kaha, ke Allah ki qasam! is taqseem mein na to adl ko malhooz rakha gaya hai aur na Allah ki khushnoodii ka khayal hua. maine kaha ke Allah ki qism ! iski khabar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zaroor doonga . chunanche main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua, aur aapko uski khabar di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sun kar farmaya ''agar Allah aur uska rasool bhi adl na karey to phir kon adl karega. Allah Taala Musa (Alaihissalam) par raham farmaai ke unko logon ke hath us se bhi zyada takleef pahunchi lekin unhon-ne sabr kya.''"
3151,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko jo zameen inayat farmai thi, mein usmein se guthliyaan (so kabhi khajoorein) apne sar par laya karti thi. wo jagah mere ghar se 2 mail farsakh ki 2 tehai par thi. abu-Zamra ne Hisham se bayan kya aur unhon-ne apne bap se (mursalan) bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko bani Nazir ki araazii mein se aik zameen qat'aa ke taur par di thii."
3152,"umr ne yahood w nasara ko sar zameene-hijaaz se nikal kar dusri jagah basaa diya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab khaibar fateh kya to aap ka bhi irada hua tha ke yahudiyon ko yahan se nikal diya jaey. jab aap ne fateh paai to us waqt wahan ki kuchh zameen yahudiyon ke qabzey mein hi thi aur aksar zameen paighambar (Alaihissalam) aur musalmanon ke qabzey mein thi. lekin phir yahudiyon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhaast ki, aap zameen unhiin ke paas rehney dein. wo (kheton aur baaghon mein) kaam kya karengey aur aadhi paidawar lengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''achchha jab tak ham chaahengey us waqt tak ke liye tumhen is shart par yahan rehney dengey. chunanche ye log wahin rahe aur phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein apne daure-khilaafat main (musalmanon ke khilaf unke fitnon aur saazishon ki wjah se yahood khaibar ko) teemaa ya Areehaa ki taraf nikal diya tha.''"
3153,"ham khaibar ke mahal ka muhaasra kiye huey they. kisi shakhs ne aik kuppii phenkii jis mein charbi bhari hui thi. main usey leney ke liye lapkaa, lekin mud kar jo dekha to paas hi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maujood they. main sharm se pani paanii ho gaya."
3154,(Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein) jangon mein hamein shehad aur angoor milta tha. ham usey usi waqt kha letey (taqseem ke liye utha na rakhtey) .
3155,jang khaibar ke mauqe par faaqon par faaqey honey lagey. aakhir jis din khaibar fateh hua to (maale-ghaneemat mein) gharelu gadhey bhi hamein miley. chunanche unhein zabah karke (pakaanaa shuru kar diya gaya) jab haandiyon mein josh aaney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadii ne elaan kya ke haandiyon ko ulat 2 aur gharelu gadhey ke gosht mein se kuchh na khaao. Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke kuchh logon ne is par kaha ke ghaaliban Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isliye rok diya hai ke abhi tak usmein se khums nahi nikala gaya tha. lekin kuchh doosrey sahaba ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gadhey ka gosht qatae taur par haram qarar diya hai. (shebaanii ne bayan kya ke) maine Saeed-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey qatae taur par haram kar diya tha.
